cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.GR, cs.HC 

The paper deals with face classification using 3D morphable face models and collaborative representation-based classification. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) categories. Additionally, the use of 3D models and rendering techniques may also make it relevant to the multimedia (cs.MM) and graphics (cs.GR) categories. Finally, the paper discusses the potential applications of the proposed method in human-computer interaction (cs.HC), which could also be a relevant sub-category.
